trategic-bombers-in-the-gulf-the-u-s-flexes-its-muscles/0000018b-cf7d-dffa-adef-ef7dfd4c0000</link><description>凭借数十架战斗机、数百枚巡航导弹和两架超音速重型轰炸机，美国可以在短时间内打击伊朗的任何目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 21:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aircraft-carrier-offshore-iran-strategic-bombers-in-the-gulf-the-u-s-flexes-its-muscles/0000018b-cf7d-dffa-adef-ef7dfd4c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拒绝国际社会允许通过其领土向加沙提供援助的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-down-international-request-to-allow-gaza-aid-via-its-territory/0000018b-cf74-dffa-adef-ef74efb00000</link><description>以色列拒绝允许援助通过凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，其根源在于其希望脱离加沙所有平民方面，以及内塔尼亚胡对政治危机的恐惧。一位西方外交官告诉《国土报》，“我们理解以色列的担忧，但我们正在努力避免加沙发生人道主义灾难”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 20:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-down-international-request-to-allow-gaza-aid-via-its-territory/0000018b-cf74-dffa-adef-ef74efb00000</guid></item><item><title>“现在，现在，现在，所有人”：以色列人质家庭的痛苦和恐惧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-14/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-families-of-kidnapped-hostages-fear-that-time-is-running-out/0000018b-cea7-d168-a3ef-dfff02e60000</link><description>随着时间一天天、几周地过去，哈马斯关押者的亲属显然已经失去了耐心，双方仍未达成任何协议，也没有任何认真的谈判努力。所以，已经达到了一个临界点</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 20:07:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-14/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-families-of-kidnapped-hostages-fear-that-time-is-running-out/0000018b-cea7-d168-a3ef-dfff02e60000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日袭击后，约 20 万人在华盛顿特区集会支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/around-200-000-rally-in-washington-d-c-in-support-of-israel-in-wake-of-october-7-attack/0000018b-cf64-df9a-ab8b-dfec6acb0000</link><description>发言者向来自全国各地的支持者发表讲话，他们举着印有袭击受害者、仍被扣押在加沙的人质面孔的标语牌，以及支持以色列和谴责哈马斯的口号</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 19:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/around-200-000-rally-in-washington-d-c-in-support-of-israel-in-wake-of-october-7-attack/0000018b-cf64-df9a-ab8b-dfec6acb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列MK呼吁西方“欢迎”来自加沙的难民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/israeli-mks-publish-plan-to-transfer-gazans-to-europe-to-alleviate-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-ce7c-d168-a3ef-dffeed320000</link><description>在《华尔街日报》的一篇文章中，来自联盟和反对派的两位议员表示，将数万名加沙人转移到欧洲是对加沙人民表现出同情心的“道义责任和机会”。极右翼部长斯莫特里奇和本格维尔很快表示支持</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 16:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/israeli-mks-publish-plan-to-transfer-gazans-to-europe-to-alleviate-humanitarian-crisis/0000018b-ce7c-d168-a3ef-dffeed320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列俘虏家属对政府越来越不耐烦，开始为期五天的游行前往耶路撒冷，要求立即解决人质问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-set-out-on-5-day-march-to-jlem-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018b-ce70-dffa-adef-ee7096200000</link><description>随着时间的推移，这些家庭的语气明显变得更加尖锐，因为他们看到并担心军事目标和外交利益被优先考虑到他们认为政府的首要责任——让亲人回家</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 16:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-set-out-on-5-day-march-to-jlem-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018b-ce70-dffa-adef-ee7096200000</guid></item><item><title>“类似于病毒”：虚假信息成为以色列与哈马斯战争致命的新战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/similar-to-a-virus-disinformation-becomes-deadly-new-front-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-cde9-dd11-a19f-edfd51180000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯之间在传统媒体和社交媒体上就 10 月 7 日大屠杀和随后的战争展开的斗争不仅是为了影响公众舆论，也是为了在新闻报道本身中播下不信任的种子</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 15:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/similar-to-a-virus-disinformation-becomes-deadly-new-front-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-cde9-dd11-a19f-edfd51180000</guid></item><item><title>“利用犹太人的痛苦”：欧洲极右翼如何利用犹太人、穆斯林和加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-jewish-pain-how-europes-far-right-is-exploiting-jews-muslims-and-the-gaza-war/0000018b-ca31-dd30-a5ff-eff10c840000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯之间的战争已经过去一个多月了，极右翼欧洲政党正在寻找机会将自己定位为犹太社区的朋友，同时谴责穆斯林移民的“危险”。政治学家表示这种拥抱不会持续太久</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 14:20:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-jewish-pain-how-europes-far-right-is-exploiting-jews-muslims-and-the-gaza-war/0000018b-ca31-dd30-a5ff-eff10c840000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中残酷的性暴力被忽视？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-14/ty-article-podcast/why-is-the-cruel-sexual-violence-of-the-october-7-hamas-attack-being-ignored/0000018b-cdbe-d423-affb-ffbfe0d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-14/ty-article-podcast/why-is-the-cruel-sexual-violence-of-the-october-7-hamas-attack-being-ignored/0000018b-cdbe-d423-affb-ffbfe0d20000</guid></item><item><title>前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾在激烈的电视对峙中拒绝称哈马斯为恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/jeremy-corbyn-refuses-to-call-hamas-a-terror-organization-in-heated-tv-standoff/0000018b-cdd6-df9a-ab8b-dfde64960000</link><description>这位长期以来一直受到反犹太主义指控的英国前工党党魁在出现在皮尔斯·摩根的节目中时回避了有关哈马斯恐怖组织地位的 15 个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/jeremy-corbyn-refuses-to-call-hamas-a-terror-organization-in-heated-tv-standoff/0000018b-cdd6-df9a-ab8b-dfde64960000</guid></item><item><title>“我们有 83 个早产儿。他们会死”：以色列必须重新考虑袭击希法医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-have-83-premature-babies-they-will-die-israel-must-rethink-attacking-al-shifa/0000018b-cdc8-d423-affb-ffeb9bdd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 13:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-have-83-premature-babies-they-will-die-israel-must-rethink-attacking-al-shifa/0000018b-cdc8-d423-affb-ffeb9bdd0000</guid></item><item><title>音乐变成枪声之前的那一刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/drawing-the-moment-before-the-music-turned-to-gunfire/0000018b-cd2e-d518-a39b-ff3f91c20000</link><description>艺术家 Andres Gurwicz 使用毛笔根据 Nova 音乐节创作作品，该音乐节在 10 月 7 日变成了残酷屠杀和酷刑的场所</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/drawing-the-moment-before-the-music-turned-to-gunfire/0000018b-cd2e-d518-a39b-ff3f91c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡尔姆开火，造成七名巴勒斯坦人死亡，三人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-three-critically-wounded-by-israeli-fire-in-west-bank-city/0000018b-cd9c-d423-affb-ffbfdfd90000</link><description>除了以色列国防军在图尔卡姆 (Tul Karm) 无人机袭击造成的伤亡之外，希伯伦附近一名 20 岁的巴勒斯坦男子在一名士兵附近拔出一把刀后被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-palestinians-killed-three-critically-wounded-by-israeli-fire-in-west-bank-city/0000018b-cd9c-d423-affb-ffbfdfd90000</guid></item><item><title>民调显示，随着战争愈演愈烈，以色列人对内塔尼亚胡的信任度直线下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/as-war-rages-israelis-trust-in-netanyahu-hits-rock-bottom-polls-find/0000018b-cd86-dd11-a19f-edf6f2b00000</link><description>巴伊兰大学研究人员进行的一项民意调查询问以色列人对加沙战争信息和决策的信任度。结果显示，不到 4% 的人信任内塔尼亚胡；以色列国防军发言人哈加里被评为“最可靠”人物</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/as-war-rages-israelis-trust-in-netanyahu-hits-rock-bottom-polls-find/0000018b-cd86-dd11-a19f-edf6f2b00000</guid></item><item><title>伊恩·布雷默：“内塔尼亚胡的自恋极大地伤害了以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ian-bremmer-netanyahus-narcissism-has-greatly-harmed-israel/0000018b-b4e8-d3c1-a39b-bee980d20000</link><description>战略专家伊恩·布雷默认为，尽管哈马斯的残酷袭击造成了创伤，但加沙战争不会危及以色列的存在。他还指出了如果地面战争持续太久的风险</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 12:04:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ian-bremmer-netanyahus-narcissism-has-greatly-harmed-israel/0000018b-b4e8-d3c1-a39b-bee980d20000</guid></item><item><title>研究表明鞋子可能早在 15 万年前就已经出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-14/ty-article/shoes-could-have-emerged-as-much-as-150-000-years-ago-study-suggests/0000018b-cd6d-df9a-ab8b-dfed4d440000</link><description>中石器时代南非岩石海滩上没有脚趾印的脚印可能表明有人穿着鞋子</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:39:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-14/ty-article/shoes-could-have-emerged-as-much-as-150-000-years-ago-study-suggests/0000018b-cd6d-df9a-ab8b-dfed4d440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争正在扰乱英国政坛。它会决定下次选举吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-is-rattling-british-politics-will-it-decide-the-next-election/0000018b-c983-d993-a1bb-f99fcf9a0000</link><description>在大规模亲巴勒斯坦集会、极右机会主义、科尔宾主义辩护以及英国反犹太主义呈指数级增长的背景下，执政的保守党和反对党工党都在以色列-加沙战争的政治风暴中航行。随着大选的临近，赌注异常高</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 11:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-is-rattling-british-politics-will-it-decide-the-next-election/0000018b-c983-d993-a1bb-f99fcf9a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>